                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The shadern draws in a deep breath and holds it, temporarily suspending their biological processes and becoming undead. The shadern gains the undead trait and becomes immune to bleed, death effects, disease, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Paralyzed]{Paralyzed}, poison, and sleep. Any such effects the shadern is currently inflicted with are suspended but take effect again once they take a breath.</p>\n<p>Death Gasp lasts as long as the shadern holds their breath (up to 8 rounds).</p>"
                },
